content: After defeating them, the fox gaui will transform into Pingping the Bull King's daughter, and thank you for saving her. Once the cutscene is over, you'll receive your rewards for defeating Quick as Fire, Fast as Wind and the next Keeper's Shrine will be available to you, if you follow the path to the left and up the stairs.

The content is as follows:
After defeating them, the fox gaui will transform into Pingping the Bull King's daughter, and thank you for saving her. Once the cutscene is over, you'll receive your rewards for defeating Quick as Fire, Fast as Wind and the next Keeper's Shrine will be available to you, if you follow the path to the left and up the stairs.
